        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is Jasper AI worth $59/seat?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "For marketing teams of 3+ with established brand voice needs — yes. For solo creators — no. Cheaper tools like Writesonic ($16/mo) or Junia AI ($15/mo) deliver comparable raw output. The premium is paid for brand voice training, collaboration, and enterprise polish." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Does Jasper AI write SEO content?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "It writes content. SEO scoring requires the Surfer SEO integration (separate subscription, $99+/mo) or manual optimization against keyword research from another tool. Jasper alone is not an SEO platform — it's an AI writer." }},
