          </table>
        </div>

        <p>Annual billing saves about 20%. Surfer SEO add-on is $99+/mo (separate billing). Business tier requires a sales call and typically lands $15k+/year for mid-market teams.</p>

        <h3>The real monthly cost most reviews skip</h3>
